Cell["\<\
The new description does not require the labeling of particles \[Implies] no \
redundancy of the basis state \[Implies] hence a both concise and precise \
description.\
\>", "TextNoIndent",ExpressionUUID->"323b708f-49c5-4e35-86a1-c644a10977fb"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

