   TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->"a4f7ece6-9d97-419e-884f-14a2941b23b4"],
 " are orthonormal basis states. The subscript ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox["\[PlusMinus]", TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "b05d85c5-bb63-4552-bea9-a69d4679bc1b"],
 " of the insertion or deletion operators indicates whether symmetrization \
(",
 Cell[BoxData[
