 "These two equations can be considered as the ",
 StyleBox["defining properties",
  FontWeight->"Bold"],
 " of fermion creation and annihilation operators. "
}], "TextNoIndent",ExpressionUUID->"fe3f1a58-5ce7-4d87-9941-c11b19005398"]
