 CounterBox["DisplayFormulaNumbered", "eq: 2438092776105532924"],
 ") implies the following operator identities"
}], "TextIndent",ExpressionUUID->"f29eb48f-d792-4b4e-acb9-7bbeebeec868"],

Cell[BoxData[
 FormBox[
  RowBox[{
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{"{", 
     RowBox[{
      SubsuperscriptBox["c", "\[Alpha]", "\[Dagger]"], ",", 
      SubsuperscriptBox["c", "\[Beta]", "\[Dagger]"]}], "}"}], "=", 
    RowBox[{
     RowBox[{"{", 
      RowBox[{
       SubscriptBox["c", "\[Alpha]"], ",", 
       SubscriptBox["c", "\[Beta]"]}], "}"}], "=", "0"}]}], ",", " ", 
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{"{", 
     RowBox[{
      SubscriptBox["c", "\[Alpha]"], ",", 
      SubsuperscriptBox["c", "\[Beta]", "\[Dagger]"]}], "}"}], "=", 
    RowBox[{
     SubscriptBox["\[Delta]", 
      RowBox[{"\[Alpha]", "\[VeryThinSpace]", "\[Beta]"}]], "."}]}]}], 
  TraditionalForm]], "DisplayFormulaFramed",ExpressionUUID->"5d619523-07e3-\
47cc-8447-881cd5d5c857"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "These relations can be considered as the ",
 StyleBox["algebraic definition",
  FontWeight->"Bold"],
 " of fermion creation and annihilation operators."
}], "TextNoIndent",ExpressionUUID->"1fb9553e-b11d-4516-891b-6f28fb92a36d"]
